name: Watercraft
description:
Started off with pure experimentation, a small structure of a boat was made while keeping it as simple as possible and then it is repeated in a hex grid. The concept was simple, to show boats floating on top of wire based water structure. This piece is titled watercraft as that falls under the boats category.

Technical Specifications 
Dimensions used - 6000 * 6000 pixels
Pattern Structure - Hex
Exported Image - PNG
